title: Grateful Dead Live at Hartford Civic Center on 1984-10-14

Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Dire Wolf, Little Red Rooster, Dupree's Diamond Blues, My Brother Esau, Loser, Minglewood Blues, Row Jimmy, I Need A Miracle-> Might As Well

Set 2
